title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer Season 1 iTunes SD
description:
This is the first season of Buffy the Vampire Slayer, and it should be compatible with all HD playing iOS devices:

---iPod touch 4th and 5th gen

---iPhone 4, 4s and 5

---all iPads

Resolution: Varies per episode - usually 768*576

Despite this being a low resolution programme it will not play on older iPods (sorry!) because I encoded it funnily. 

Also word of warning the first episode suffers from a horrid motion blur during some fast moving scenes, but subsequent episodes are all ok!


If you have never watched buffy I would seriously recommend it!  Its very funny!
